OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start with spells of
OL,6,Frain, this heavy at times. The rain
OL,7,Fwill turn showery into the afternoon
OL,8,Fand some areas will see some drier and
OL,9,Fbrighter spells developing. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain clearing to
OL,13,Fthe south during the evening, leaving
OL,14,Fthe region with clear spells. Chilly
OL,15,Fwith a touch of grass frost in the
OL,16,Frural north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
